ComplexKeyHashed - plan
SELECT
    __table1.k1 AS k1,
    __table1.k2 AS k2,
    __table1.payload AS payload
FROM default.f AS __table1
WHERE (__table1.k1 = _CAST(1, \'UInt64\')) AND (__table1.k2 = \'a\')
ORDER BY
    __table1.k1 ASC,
    __table1.k2 ASC,
    __table1.payload ASC
ComplexKeyHashed
1	a	x
ComplexKeyHashed, opt off
1	a	x
